    <dcterms:alternative>extraneous variable</dcterms:alternative>
    <dcterms:alternative>controlled variable</dcterms:alternative>
    <dcterms:description xml:lang="en">A control variable that is believed to alter the dependent or independent variables, but may not actually be the focus of the experiment. So that variable will be kept constant or monitored to try to minimise its effect on the experiment.</dcterms:description>
